DESCRIPTION:Speakers:
Alexis Zamkow\, Global Offering Lead - Marketing Transformation\, IBM

Peter Ng\, Americas Solution Lead - Adobe\, IBM

Seth Besmertnik\, CEO\, Conductor

Global consumer use of applications like ChatGPT has jumped 62% in just two years\, signaling the arrival of agentic commerce. Hear how IBM\, Adobe\, and Conductor collaborate to enable development and deployment of GEO-friendly content at scale.
